  "text": "ERPs allow us to monitor brain activity during the entire information-processing stream, ranging from sensory to higher cognitive processes. Therefore, during a cognitive task, ERPs allow one to identify the electrophysiological component representing the onset of a dysfunction, and then to infer the impaired cognitive stages [CITATION_1] .",
